00:19:26.580 --> 00:19:27.590
Rei!

00:19:30.270 --> 00:19:31.470
Ölmeye hazır ol!

00:19:33.900 --> 00:19:34.930
Ne?!

00:19:38.060 --> 00:19:40.650
Daha bitmedi.

00:19:44.550 --> 00:19:45.400
Ateş

